main event: Ten white lights were observed moving in a jumbled formation from north to southwest over Spokane, Washington on August 20, 1952.
interesting points: The lights were seen for about 10 seconds,There were multiple sightings reported,The control tower operator confirmed the sighting,The lights moved in a formation that was described as jumbled,Visibility was clear at 25 miles when the objects were seen.
sighted object: ten white lights in the sky
witness description: Control Power Operator at Geiger Field
